MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: This mapping loads the data from multiple source tables into Sources_Combined_key table.
MAPPING.NAME: m_FDC_SRC_COMBINED_KEY

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Extratcs the data from source event and Current
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_SKU_CURRENT_EVENT

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select TS_DIV_CODE ,SOLDTO ,BUSINESS_SEGMENT_HIERARCY ,Division ,isnull(FUTURE_DOORS,0) as FUTURE_DOORS ,FISCAL_YEAR ,FISCAL_PERIOD ,FISCAL_WEEK ,main.AS_OF_DATE_INT as AS_OF_DATE_INT ,FCST_SKU_KEY ,fdw.week_ind as week_ind, source from (select distinct TS_DIV_CODE ,SOLDTO ,BUSINESS_SEGMENT_HIERARCY ,Division ,sum(isnull(FUTURE_DOORS,0)) as FUTURE_DOORS ,FISCAL_YEAR ,FISCAL_PERIOD ,FISCAL_WEEK ,AS_OF_DATE_INT ,FCST_SKU_KEY ,Source from FDC.SKU_Current with (NOLOCK) where LCA IN ('1','6','-1','7','3','11','9','8','10') and as_of_date_int <= (SELECT as_of_date_int FROM FDC.vw_Future_Door_Week_Ind with (NOLOCK) where week_ind = 'CURWEEK') and FCST_SKU_KEY<>'UNMAPPED' and demand_driver='REPLN' group by TS_DIV_CODE,SOLDTO,BUSINESS_SEGMENT_HIERARCY,Division,FISCAL_YEAR,FISCAL_PERIOD, FISCAL_WEEK,AS_OF_DATE_INT,FCST_SKU_KEY, SOURCE ) main inner join FDC.vw_Future_Door_Week_Ind fdw on main.as_of_date_int= fdw.as_of_date_int where SOLDTO is not null and BUSINESS_SEGMENT_HIERARCY is not null and Division is not null and main.AS_OF_DATE_INT is not null and FCST_SKU_KEY is not null

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: THIS LOOKUP IS TO READ DATA FROM TARGET TO CHECK BEFORE LOAD FOR STAGE 2
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_TARGET

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT Sources_Combined_key.FCST_SKU_KEY as FCST_SKU_KEY, Sources_Combined_key.SOLDTO as SOLDTO FROM FDC.Sources_Combined_key WITH(NOLOCK)

SESSION.NAME: s_m_FDC_SRC_COMBINED_KEY_STG2

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select TS_DIV_CODE ,SOLDTO ,BUSINESS_SEGMENT_HIERARCY ,Division ,isnull(FUTURE_DOORS,0) as FUTURE_DOORS ,FISCAL_YEAR ,FISCAL_PERIOD ,FISCAL_WEEK ,main.AS_OF_DATE_INT as AS_OF_DATE_INT ,FCST_SKU_KEY ,fdw.week_ind as week_ind, SOURCE from ( select distinct TS_DIV_CODE ,SOLDTO ,BUSINESS_SEGMENT_HIERARCY ,Division ,sum(isnull(FUTURE_DOORS,0)) as FUTURE_DOORS ,FISCAL_YEAR ,FISCAL_PERIOD ,FISCAL_WEEK ,AS_OF_DATE_INT ,FCST_SKU_KEY ,SOURCE from FDC.SKU_event e with (NOLOCK) where as_of_date_int > (SELECT as_of_date_int FROM FDC.vw_Future_Door_Week_Ind with (NOLOCK) where week_ind = 'CURWEEK') and FCST_SKU_KEY<>'UNMAPPED' and( (upper(demand_driver) in ('REPLN') and upper(updated_by) in ('ETL_LOAD_HSF_EVNTS_EMSV2')) or (upper(demand_driver) in ('REPLN','EVENT') and upper(updated_by) in ('ETL_LOAD_HSF_TRAK_EVENTS','ETL_LOAD_HSF_ESS_EVENTS','ETL_LOAD_HSF_CMT_EVENTS','ETL_LOAD_HSF_EMS_EVENTS'))) group by TS_DIV_CODE,SOLDTO,BUSINESS_SEGMENT_HIERARCY,Division,FISCAL_YEAR,FISCAL_PERIOD,FISCAL_WEEK,AS_OF_DATE_INT,FCST_SKU_KEY, SOURCE ) main inner join FDC.vw_Future_Door_Week_Ind fdw on main.as_of_date_int= fdw.as_of_date_int where SOLDTO is not null and BUSINESS_SEGMENT_HIERARCY is not null and Division is not null and main.AS_OF_DATE_INT is not null and FCST_SKU_KEY is not null

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Extratcs the data from source FROM FDC.DoorCount_Updated
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_SKU_DOOR_COUNT_UPDATED

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select TS_DIV_CODE ,SOLDTO ,BUSINESS_SEGMENT_HIERARCY ,Division ,isnull(FUTURE_DOORS,0) as FUTURE_DOORS ,FISCAL_YEAR ,FISCAL_PERIOD ,FISCAL_WEEK ,main.AS_OF_DATE_INT as AS_OF_DATE_INT ,FCST_SKU_KEY ,fdw.week_ind as week_ind from (select distinct [TS_DIV_CODE] ,[SOLDTO] ,[BUSINESS_SEGMENT_HIERARCY] ,[Division] ,sum(isnull([FUTURE_DOORS],0)) as FUTURE_DOORS ,[FISCAL_YEAR] ,[FISCAL_PERIOD] ,[FISCAL_WEEK] ,[AS_OF_DATE_INT] ,[FCST_SKU_KEY] from FDC.DoorCount_Updated u with (nolock) where as_of_date_int > (SELECT [as_of_date_int] FROM FDC.vw_Future_Door_Week_Ind with (nolock) where week_ind = 'CURWEEK') and [FCST_SKU_KEY]<>'UNMAPPED' group by [TS_DIV_CODE],[SOLDTO],[BUSINESS_SEGMENT_HIERARCY],[Division],[FISCAL_YEAR],[FISCAL_PERIOD],[FISCAL_WEEK],[AS_OF_DATE_INT],[FCST_SKU_KEY] )main inner join FDC.vw_Future_Door_Week_Ind fdw on main.as_of_date_int= fdw.as_of_date_int where SOLDTO is not null and BUSINESS_SEGMENT_HIERARCY is not null and Division is not null and main.AS_OF_DATE_INT is not null and FCST_SKU_KEY is not null

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: FCST_SKU_KEY = I_FCST_SKU_KEY AND SOLDTO = I_SOLDTO AND BUSINESS_SEGMENT_HIERARCY = I_BUSINESS_SEGMENT_HIERARCY AND AS_OF_DATE_INT = I_AS_OF_DATE_INT
